text: Macdonald-Cartier may refer to: *Macdonald-Cartier Freeway, in southern Ontario, also known as Highway 401 *Macdonald-Cartier Bridge, a bridge between Ottawa, Ontario, and Gatineau, Quebec *Ottawa Macdonald–Cartier International Airport, a major Canadian airport in Ottawa *Macdonald-Cartier High School, a former Quebec high school in Saint-Hubert, Quebec, that merged with Richelieu Valley Regional High School *École secondaire Macdonald-Cartier, a French public language high school in Sudbury
title: Macdonald-Cartier
